Because of the novelty. Because of the differences. Because you *can* make something new interesting and fun with the beastial side of a humanized and uplifted race. Because you enjoy writing about it and it helps the quality of your work. Because you are inspied to do so, because you an make it work and because god knows there are already 58 thousand other shitty novels out there about some guy getting some girl with shit tier writing going high but it would be beyond impressive to make it about a guy and a fuzzy whammen, dealing with the issues between culture, learned behaviour and how they adapt to this world which may be ours or theirs.

The difference is in everything you make different. You make the characters anthros because you believe you can make something interesting, fun or just good with them as such. And making them just humans would probably make it duller than a wooden training sword.
